{"type":"message","id":"acdd44f7","parentId":"00000687","timestamp":"2026-04-01T12:38:34.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron session itself (the idle detection task). There are no other active user conversations in the last 5 minutes. I should execute the self-learning task - searching for the latest industry trends related to 道简网络's business areas: enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"d234819710e1b29eb453c67141c113d27b1008196a442ed2cc54906135cb0529"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前 cron 任务会话，无用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0axv181m2ql4_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":811,"output":131,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44923,"cost":{"input":0.00024329999999999998,"output":0.0001572,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00171993}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775047109424}}
