{"type":"message","id":"95f2116e","parentId":"c1e574ae","timestamp":"2026-04-01T12:40:03.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've successfully completed the self-learning task. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"c0e754d03872476a769c753588da41eca0a2720e7211d2d41071cfe447a9e1b6"},{"type":"text","text":"**自主学习完成** ✅\n\n**执行情况**：\n- 🕐 检测时间：2026-04-01 20:38\n- 📊 活跃对话：0（无用户活跃会话）\n- 🔍 搜索渠道：Web Search（4个关键词并行）\n- 📝 整理信息：4大行业 × 各5条关键趋势\n- 💾 保存位置：`/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**关键学习内容摘要**：\n\n| 行业 | 核心趋势 | 对道简参考价值 |\n|------|---------|--------------|\n| 企业数字化 | AI原生/Agent普及、数据驱动、双智协同组织 | 🔴 高 |\n| 智能安防 | AI大模型+全链路闭环、合规优先、生态整合 | 🔴 高 |\n| IT运维 | AIOps 3.0自治化、国产替代、ESG融合 | 🟡 中 |\n| 网络系统集成 | 零信任必选项、6700亿市场、AI驱动防御 | 🔴 高 |\n\n笔记已保存，可随时调用。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5535,"output":242,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49758,"cost":{"input":0.0016604999999999999,"output":0.0002904,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032703299999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775047195898}}
